    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a data model for Access Control Lists (ACLs).  An ACL is a user-ordered set of rules used to configure the forwarding behavior in a device.  Each rule is used to find a match on a packet and define actions that will be performed on the packet.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
